    "# Network Packet Transmission Simulator\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook simulates network packet transmission in a network. Each packet can either be delivered successfully or lost (simulated randomly). The notebook visualizes delivered vs lost packets and calculates success rate. Optional animation demonstrates the packet flow."
   ]
  },
  {
